{"tid":838641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國外交部耿爽：敦促美國停止誹謗和指責中國","createTime":"2018-09-27T09:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T04:13:35.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6878c732916db3a06baccbed5386072a4288244b","tid":838641,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20180927/s00010/067798feec29493cdb5355441f57f5c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20180927%2Fs00010%2F067798feec29493cdb5355441f57f5c5.jpg&h=73d09e26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人耿爽在例行發布會上表示，就有關中國試圖插手美國中期選舉的言論，敦促美國停止誹謗和指責中國。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽指，中方一貫奉行不干涉別國內政原則，中方不接受任何無端指責，敦促美國停止錯誤的言行。<span style=\"color: red;\">又指，《中國日報》在美國報紙上登廣告是正常合作，以此指責中國干預美國選舉是牽強的、錯誤的。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1538038683417&amp;issue=20180927\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1538038683417%26issue%3D20180927&d=MMfzIUeDDF2SfcWtqNfQN%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=84299532\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1538038683417%26issue%3D20180927&h=ff23d596\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1538038683417&amp;issue=20180927</a>"},{"pid":"fa144976cf9686db1f4825f85dc239c880224e59","tid":838641,"uid":13115,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:30:28.000Z","msg":"做完唔敢認?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0641a98be3c2a3a7e111a48a35e4f5a8a5758af4","tid":838641,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:31:59.000Z","msg":"打未啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98abba8038cd44f4bda30934304407e1e2e4d818","tid":